{"_path":"/maps/_policy/industrial-parks-guide","_dir":"_policy","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"工业园区高质量发展指引","description":"工信部、国家发改委联合印发的工业园区发展政策，明确\"特色化、集约化、数智化、绿色化、规范化\"五化发展方向","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"政策背景"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"政策背景"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《工业园区高质量发展指引》由工业和信息化部、国家发展改革委于 2025 年 9 月联合印发（工信部联规〔2025〕189 号），\n旨在引导工业园区从\"量的快速增长\"迈向\"质的有效提升\"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当前工业园区面临的核心问题："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"同质化竞争"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：各地园区产业定位雷同，全国化工园区超过 700 家，存在\"产业同质化、招商内卷化\"现象"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"土地低效利用"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：存量工业用地面积前 30 名城市的低效用地总和约 1240.78 平方公里"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"散乱污\"企业"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：分布零散、手续不全、环保设施缺失的企业对生态环境造成压力"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.news.cn/house/20251013/2597daa803f7451196d0ae60e5b9b379/c.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"工业园区有了高质量发展路线图"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.gov.cn/govweb/zhengce/zhengceku/202509/content_7041869.htm","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"政策原文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"三主导产业红线是破解同质化竞争的制度创新"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\"三主导产业\"红线是破解同质化竞争的制度创新？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"《指引》首次从中央层面明确